data.description:
Welcome to your own Gorgeous Private Oasis!  This well cared for Single Story home sits on just under 1/2 acre, at the end of a quiet street in Old Lakeway, with views of the Hill Country from the backyard.  Enter the home and you are greeted by a spacious great room, formal dining, and a huge designer kitchen with tons of storage.  Walls of windows let in natural light and provide a beautiful view overlooking the sparkling pool, hot tub, and covered stone patio.  The pool has a large beach landing and two water features, which along with the luscious tropical landscaping, make you feel like you are living at a fabulous resort.   
            The new homeowner will appreciate that the big ticket items have been done recently and are still under warranty such as: a new Water Heater 4/21, a new Heat Pump installed in 2020, a new pool pump,  a new pump for the Polaris, and, the concrete tile roof was recently inspected by Kid Roofing and is in excellent condition.
            
            The home is conveniently located across the street from the 5th Tee on the Live Oak Golf Course, 3 miles to the Yaupon Golf Course, and 1 mile to the Lakeway Swim Center and World of Tennis.  It is also only minutes away from the Lakeway Airport and the Lakeway Market which has fabulous wine, a craft beer bar, and delicious Breakfast/Dinner takeout.  10/23 Appraisal available.
